race.comment: CASCAN (10) resumes. Finished ninth over 1400m at Armidale at her most recent appearance on October 14. Rates highly and should take a hand in the finish. MAGIC SORCERER (2) turned in a nice effort to score two runs ago at Gilgandra. Safely held last time out when eighth over 1300m at Gunnedah. Has the ability to take this out. POP QUIZ (7) was in the money two starts back at Quirindi but was unable to repeat the effort last time when sixth over 1400m at Glen Innes. Nicely placed to make amends. GOLD SMILES (3) was racing well without winning, finishing in the money on two consecutive occasions, before finishing seventh last time out over 1000m at Gunnedah. Keep safe.
